fields.name: Arizona Original Bootcut Jeans
fields.description: Bootcut jeans in our just-right original fit are comfortable and look great too. 5-pocket style sits below waist straight fit through seat and thigh bootcut leg 18" leg opening cotton washable imported extended sizes and washes available online only

fields.name: Vintage Leather Jacket
fields.description: Stay stylish with this vintage-inspired leather jacket. Made from genuine leather, it features a classic design with a zippered front, multiple pockets, and a comfortable fit. Perfect for any casual or semi-formal occasion.

fields.name: Elegant Floral Dress
fields.description: Step out in style with this elegant floral dress. The beautiful floral print and flowy design make it perfect for special occasions or a day out. Made from high-quality fabric, it offers comfort and sophistication.
